What is your overall assessment of this course?
Do you expect to use this class for credit toward your major, or toward a pre-professional program?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This was a unique class in that each student wrote and directed his/her own solo performance. Both the teacher and instructors were great. We also were able to work on improv technique.

Yes, I'd recommend it, but make sure that you stay on top of the work and motivate yourself because it is really your project, so it's up to you. There were very intense periods of work, and then lighter loads at different times throughout the semester.
